high_descs: turn around and walk to the sidetable
walk to the knife on the table
pick up knife from the bread
take bread to the bed
cut bread into slices
Put the knife on the bed.
Pick up slice of bread from the bed.
Bring the slice of bread to the plate on the bed.
Place the slice of bread on the bowl.
pick up bread from the bowl
walk into the table with bowl.
Place the plate on the sidetable.
Stare at the bowl and sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Get slice of bread on the side table.

high_descs: Walk straight towards the sidetable.
Walk to your right and pick up the knife.
Move towards the bread on the brown table.
Pick up the knife from the brown table.
Take a left turn and a right towards the bed.
Move towards the white bed.
Slice the bread on the bed with knife.
Keep the bread on the right corner of the bed.
Take a slice of bread from the bowl.
Take a right turn towards the bread bowl.
Keep the piece of bread in the bowl on the bed.
Pick up the bowl with bread piece from the sidetable.
Keep the bowl with bread piece on the sidetable near the bed.
anns.task_desc: Go to bedroom, take the knife, slice the bread, Place it in a bowl and keep it on the SideTable.

high_descs: Walk straight and enter into the bedroom. Then turn left to reach the sidetable.
Take the knife from the top of the mini table.
Move little bit towards left to reach the bread.
Cut the bread loaf into pieces which is kept on the top of the bed.
Turn left by facing the bed.
Put the knife above a bowl which is on the bed next to bread loaf pieces.
Now turn towards the bed.
Take a bread piece from the cut bread.
Little bit move towards right and stand in front of the bowl table.
Put the bread slice on the bowl which is below the knife.
Take the bowl along with the bread piece.
Little bit turn towards left and again turn right to face the sidetable.
Put the bowl on the sidetable along with the bread piece.
anns.task_desc: Put the bread piece in the bowl and place it on the side table.
